#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Next Level Gift</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Regal de nivell següent</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Next Level Gift</term>"
msgstr "<term>&nbsp;Regal de nivell següent</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the next level of the game immediately."
msgstr "Obre immediatament el nivell següent del joc."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Les estratègies i consells"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If possible, it is usually a good idea to send the ball above the bricks, "
"doing so you will have a smaller chance of losing the ball. Sometimes you "
"need to first make a small hole in the layer of brick to accomplish this. "
"The smaller the hole, the smaller the chance the balls comes back down."
msgstr ""
"Si és possible, sol ser una bona idea enviar la bola per sobre dels maons, "
"d'aquesta manera tindreu menys possibilitats de perdre-la. De vegades, per a "
"aconseguir això, primer haureu de fer un petit forat a la capa de maons. Com "
"més petit sigui el forat, menor serà la possibilitat que les boles tornin a "
"baixar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When catching the add ball gift it is wise to not fire it right away but to "
"keep in instead, in case the other balls are lost. It is also advisable to "
"not catch a sticky bar gift in such a case, as doing so would force you to "
"fire all balls."
msgstr ""
"Quan s'atrapa el regal d'afegir una bola, és aconsellable no disparar-la "
"immediatament, sinó mantenir-la pel cas que es perdin les altres boles. En "
"aquest cas també és aconsellable no atrapar un regal de barra enganxosa, ja "
"que en fer-ho us obligarà a disparar totes les boles."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When receiving a next level gift you may not want to catch it if you know "
"that there are add life gifts in the level."
msgstr ""
"Quan es rep un regal de nivell següent, és possible que no el vulgueu rebre "
"si sabeu que en aquest nivell hi ha regals per a afegir vides."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In levels where there are a lot of hidden bricks there may be a way to win "
"the level without having to destroy most of them."
msgstr ""
"En els nivells on hi ha molts maons ocults, pot haver-hi una forma de "
"guanyar el nivell sense haver-ne de destruir la majoria."

